玩到頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:40:53.000Z","msg":"但好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed31b077ab3dc0b3faf3c43b77ff80405e0ad4b1","tid":2377130,"uid":318046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a39554bcebe9f6ef5de56521de95558f09efacc8","tid":2377130,"uid":8495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c92d63e9bf129bd918982d8defcfbabf592b43","tid":2377130,"uid":37697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"隻game絕對係2020最top<br />\n但問題係傳統槍game已經唔hit<br />\n<br />\n玩嘅人少，認受性低，GOTY某程度上係popular contest<br />\n所以會輸"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"但我覺得呢隻槍game 好特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"槍game界忍者"},{"pid":"9ed2335d6641288ba571426c3800b2fe192090e3","tid":2377130,"uid":8495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2b590bdfea4203664f966fbd40ea774b7716a8","tid":2377130,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d50a571974f4e3dcc66340609d9427860b012a4c","tid":2377130,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T12:26:01.000Z","msg":"睇完解說都唔係好明個故事講乜<br />\n係咪大概就係話男主比自己個世界放棄咗之後去咗宜家呢個世界但係又要救翻啲人類？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T18:10:33.000Z","msg":"我冇細心睇故仔 大概應該係咁<br />\nEternal有重要劇情既位得揭發左新Doom既主角,其實係舊doom既主角黎<br />\n舊doom個主角大概就係話佢係咁殺惡魔,<br />\n殺到入埋地獄<br />\n舊版故事應該到呢到<br />\nEternal中間就有講班中世紀裝人係地獄發現到佢重傷<br />\n之後捉佢返黎做士兵,幫佢地手打惡魔<br />\n應該都係打打下中伏,比人封左係個棺材<br />\n就到到新版1集一開波個到,講個棺比人類既火星研究所拎左返去<br />\n<br />\n新版個世界設定都係話<br />\n海登(個白色機械人)搵到惡魔啲資源<br />\n搞到惡魔入侵左佢地個星球<br />\n新版第1集就講惡魔入侵左火星<br />\n第1集個尾講海登利用完主角就掉走佢<br />\n第2集就講入侵埋地球,<br />\n遊戲開始之前既劇情話海登整左啲軍隊同裝備抵抗惡魔<br />\n大概咁上下<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇講錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472043a44bdc53886ed35245a3e3ae2cc4144da9","tid":2377130,"uid":308398,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T18:50:59.000Z","msg":"玩咗兩個鐘就退咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知係我廢定點，啲怪太坦射好多槍都唔死，啲制太多記唔晒。仲有可能頭幾關未有boss打，啲soundtrack聽落好一般。同埋隻角色行得有啲慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得dash冇得slide<br />\nDoom Eternal係隻幾好嘅驚，但小弟唔太識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9592f2be97871448853172cceb3b3012dfb3e2","tid":2377130,"uid":323922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"472043a44bdc53886ed35245a3e3ae2cc4144da9","tid":2377130,"uid":308398,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T18:50:59.000Z","msg":"玩咗兩個鐘就退咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知係我廢定點，啲怪太坦射好多槍都唔死，啲制太多記唔晒。仲有可能頭幾關未有boss打，啲soundtrack聽落好一般。同埋隻角色行得有啲慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得dash冇得slide<br />\nDoom Eternal係隻幾好嘅驚，但小弟唔太識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T18:54:11.000Z","msg":"你係咪當左隻game係CoD或者Uncharted嗰啲cover shooter玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多怪你衝埋去射兩槍就死"},{"pid":"951cbed19ac0eb125bfb097510567732b94e3665","tid":2377130,"uid":308398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd9592f2be97871448853172cceb3b3012dfb3e2","tid":2377130,"uid":323922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"472043a44bdc53886ed35245a3e3ae2cc4144da9","tid":2377130,"uid":308398,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T18:50:59.000Z","msg":"玩咗兩個鐘就退咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知係我廢定點，啲怪太坦射好多槍都唔死，啲制太多記唔晒。仲有可能頭幾關未有boss打，啲soundtrack聽落好一般。同埋隻角色行得有啲慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"h